00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:20,880
♪Which mountain turned away and forgot?♪

569
00:39:21,520 --> 00:39:25,560
♪Even if time flows endlessly♪

570
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:28,870
♪It hasn’t erased your trace♪

571
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:31,820
♪But this path is always rugged♪

572
00:39:32,050 --> 00:39:36,800
♪People gaze at mottled illusions♪

573
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:41,770
♪Through a door,
glimpsing heaven and earth♪

574
00:39:49,530 --> 00:39:53,410
♪Even if the colors have long blurred♪

575
00:39:57,460 --> 00:40:02,690
♪Even if they’ve long
dissolved into chaos♪

576
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:11,580
♪Forgetting the reason,
forgetting the outcome♪

577
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:12,550
♪Why not forget it all?♪

578
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:15,260
♪That scar, that shackle♪

579
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:19,560
♪Let the storm sing praises,
storm, storm, storm♪

580
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:24,410
♪Witness a brave heart shining bright♪

581
00:40:24,580 --> 00:40:27,290
♪Forgetting the reason,
forgetting the outcome♪

582
00:40:27,500 --> 00:40:31,290
♪But holding on even tighter,
no matter the ease or adversity♪

583
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:36,050
♪Still stubborn, unrepentant,
storm, storm, storm♪

584
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:40,800
♪Forgetting the return date,
but not this moment♪
